room_title: Escape room "Sherlock Holmes and the Hound of the Baskervilles" by Mystery Escape Room in St. George
room_address: 46 W St. George Blvd. St. George, UT 84770
room_description: Years ago Sherlock Holmes was able to solve the mystery of the hound at the old Baskerville mansion. But a mystery still remains. Who killed old man Baskerville all those years earlier. There has to be clues left behind. Once you are in the old hunting lodge, see what you can uncover to solve the mystery that has baffled all for so many years.
